{"tid":1609093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈，唔好再叫PoPo、黑警、毅進仔，俾個襯得返佢地既名俾佢地！","createTime":"2019-10-01T13:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T14:05:30.000Z","uid":278180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"faf21bca1df6d86a364a28c90401ee6cd0f4eca1","tid":1609093,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:32:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">賣港賊！</span></span><br />\n全香港咁多區o係10.1人話俾全世界知，我地唔撚會幫中共依個仆街政權慶祝！我地係香港人，一個有良知，仍然會頑抗世界最大既黑社會－－－中共既小島！<br />\n依班港共既走狗警察，用我地納稅人既錢出糧，用真子彈射鳩我地既下一代！？<br />\n葉繼歡拎撚住支AK，都係射腳。今日你班仆街賣港賊衝入人群向個細路心口開槍！？<br />\n<br />\n全香港人唔怕死、唔怕拉、唔拍無前途，攬炒咁戰鬥緊！你班仆街為左好似光頭柒警長上京受勳，拎真槍射鳩我地！？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">賣港賊！屌你老母！一世唔原熟賣港賊！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n推撚爆佢！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"f0ae8dbbfee3f31f7ed914b482bee6c011e63110","tid":1609093,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ad64ea3a280c3e2d6d48e6e6b5413a02f94b750","tid":1609093,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff306466ab90daec778c516f45708a73ae007d48","tid":1609093,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90b0999000357e89f45e0ec2b624f19658aaa0a7","tid":1609093,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58e34ef32984d7078665a69f2811d0900bc25727","tid":1609093,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:35:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9790b740205f3f090b3ed429a9cd230d9cef5b59","tid":1609093,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f0eadb160404461e66fe0aef5966831daa30e23","tid":1609093,"uid":278180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"